title: Pocono sports memories: Name the Game, No. 188
text: Posted Oct. 26, 2015 at 8:02 AM Updated at 8:04 AM Posted Oct. 26, 2015 at 8:02 AM Updated at 8:04 AM • Gallery: Name the Game, No. 188 » Social News Do you recognize the wrestlers shown in this 1960s photo? Share your knowledge and appreciation of local sports history with our readers. Responses will appear in the following Monday's newspaper. Mail typewritten answers to Name the Game, Pocono Record Library, 511 Lenox St., Stroudsburg, PA 18360; fax 570-421-6284; or email library@poconorecord.com. Include your name, town and phone number (not for publication). Description of the photo and accompanying memories should be no longer than 50 words. poconorecord.com Posted Oct. 26, 2015 at 8:02 AM Updated at 8:04 AM
